cars.name: Swift Dezire
cars.details: Maruti Swift Dezire Tour is a 5-seater car. The car is available in petrol manual and cng manual configurations in White colour only and 2 variants.Swift Dzire Tour is a fuel efficient car with petrol mileage of 23.15 kmpl and CNG mileage of 31.12 km/kg.
